ARIAS SANCHEZ, OSCAR; COSTA RICA -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- NICARAGUA; COSTA RICA 
-- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- EL SALVADOR; FARABUNDO MARTI NATIONAL LIBERATION FRONT 
(EL SALVADOR) 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
