<HEADLINE>
<P>
12-YEAR-OLD BOY FOUND DEAD ATOP ELEVATOR CAR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
NEW YORK 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A 12-year-old boy was found dead atop a Harlem apartment building's elevator 
car, where officials believe he had been playing. The body of Walter McMillan 
was found Saturday evening when the car was at the 27th floor, a Housing 
Authority police spokesman said. The cause of death was not released 
immediately. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
