<P>
General Dynamics Claims False Charges: General Dynamics sued the U.S. 
government in federal court in Los Angeles on Tuesday for $29.2 million, 
claiming that the company was falsely charged with defense fraud because 
federal auditors misinterpreted billings for an anti-aircraft gun. The company 
claims government auditors negligently misinterpreted its Army contract. (Filed 
