backers of cityhood for Laguna Hills are about to try again. . . . Their first 
attempt on the June ballot failed by less than 1% because of a strong no vote 
from Leisure World. . . . Backers say they will not include Leisure World in 
their next incorporation attempt. . . . Had they done that in June, 
incorporation would have passed by more than 8 to 1. Dana Parsons and Steve 
Emmons 
